vmwSystemMIB.name: vmwSystemMIB

revisions.description: Add vmwProdPatch managed object to report patch level
Add to comments the Managed Object Browser (MOB) URLs which provide data this MIB module exposes.
This is the first revision in SMIv2 format. One object (vmwProdOID) has been dropped from the original SMIv1 version as it duplicates sysObjectId from SNMPv2-MIB.
